18/01/2009
BOLGNA, Italy -- Police announced on Saturday (January 17th) they smashed an international drug smuggling gang and arrested 18 people, including 15 Albanians, in an operation that began in August.
Investigators say the gang supplied heroin to the Bologna area.
A total of 90kg of heroin from Albania was seized.
(MIA, Makfax - 17/01/09)
